Leah Ayres https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leah_Ayres 0 Leah Ayres (born May 28, 1957) is an American actress, best known for her role as Janice Kent in the sports thriller Bloodsport and as Valerie Bryson on the daytime serial The Edge of Night.
